Hedy Burress https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hedy_Burress 0 Heather Elizabeth "Hedy" Burress is an American actress. She had a starring role in the film Foxfire as Maddy, and later landed roles in television shows Boston Common and E.R.. In the video game world, she is best known as the English voice of leading character Yuna in Final Fantasy X and its sequel Final Fantasy X-2. She reprised her role as Yuna in World of Final Fantasy, released in 2016. Heather_Elizabeth_"_Hedy_"_Burress is an_American_actress .
